 \mathbb{E}[f(X,Y)]=\sum_{x,y}f(x,y)\cdot P(X=x, Y=y). 
 \mathbb{E}[X+Y]=\sum_{x,y}(x+y)P(X=x,Y=y)=\sum_{x,y}xP(X=x,Y=y)+\sum_{x,y}yP(X=x,Y=y). 
